title: Ranked Games
body:
Can someone help me/give tips for me to get better in ranked, every game i play my team is good late but then late game and they suck
Im silver 4
Help out a brother :D

replies.body: Tell them to group if they do well early. A 15 minute mid push, the enemy team won't react - they don't in Diamond so don't think they would in silver LOL.
Ima take that advice, even if he doesn't. Thanks mate
